Paragraph.Span: Thank you for answering these questions about your child. The answers will help your doctor provide better quality of care. If your child is age 11 or older, he/she should answer the questions privately. Answers are confidential, but if you prefer not to answer that is allowed. You may want to talk about these questions with your doctor.
